WEBVTT

00:08.006 --> 00:11.917
In a city filled with stunning Byzantine and Ottoman architecture,...

00:12.319 --> 00:17.702
...one masterpiece stands head and shoulders above all others: Hagia Sophia.

00:22.223 --> 00:24.408
Formerly the greatest church in Christendom,...

00:24.854 --> 00:29.631
...this magnificent domed building was converted into a mosque in the 15th century...

